title: Transfusions
description:
Transfusions is a love story between Dylan, a media student, and a young, arrogant vampire called Joa. Their relationship develops from threats and bickering into a gentle but passionate romance. 

Status: Ongoing

Tags: Manga, Yaoi, Vampires, Drama, Romance
